            <title>[OAK-2068] Lucene index: &quot;reindex&quot; property is automatically set to true</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/OAK-2068</link>
                <project id="12313221" key="OAK">Jackrabbit Oak</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;For some reason, the &quot;reindex&quot; property of Lucene is automatically set to &quot;true&quot; even after re-indexes seems to be finished.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
